      <event start="T656-066" end="T221">[nerazumljivo] In to velikega, to velikega. </event>
      <event start="T221" end="T661-408">Smo meli enega od strica ... </event>
      <event start="T661-408" end="T662-767">Smo meli ... </event>
      <event start="T662-767" end="T665-533">smo imeli strica, ki je bil brat od moj() mojga woča. </event>
      <event start="T665-533" end="T412">Ki je bil ku da bi malo bolj tko specialist za, za </event>
      <event start="T412" end="T671-585">ubivat, je znal [nerazumljivo]. </event>
      <event start="T671-585" end="T674-093">[smeh] Je bil pa lopov. </event>
      <event start="T674-093" end="T225">[smeh] Ja. </event>
      <event start="T225" end="T226">Ki je hodu [nerazumljivo], </event>
      <event start="T226" end="T679-891">on je tega prasca mesaru, mesaru, nonštop, nonštop. </event>
      <event start="T679-891" end="T688-232">In zmerej, k@ je pršu, [smeh] je nejga prostur [smeh] za skr(), za skrt, za skrt malu več deleč od tega prasca. </event>
      <event start="T688-232" end="T228">Jes sem to znal, </event>
      <event start="T228" end="T689-752">ne. </event>
      <event start="T689-752" end="T413">Ma kaj če, kur wotrok, </event>
      <event start="T413" end="T229">kaj sm tel rečt. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T229" end="T692-165">Nanka me ni brigalo. </event>
      <event start="T692-165" end="T230">Tu ne. </event>
      <event start="T230" end="T231">In tašno in podobno je blo, </event>
      <event start="T231" end="T694-748">ne. </event>
      <event start="T694-748" end="T695-855">In pol je seveda, </event>
      <event start="T695-855" end="T232">pol je tel j@s. </event>
      <event start="T232" end="T233">Pa je pršu uni: </event>
      <event start="T233" end="T234">"Ubivajo prasca pr Morato, </event>
      <event start="T234" end="T235">ubivajo prasca, </event>
      <event start="T235" end="T236">ubivajo prasca oni." </event>
      <event start="T236" end="T700-521">Pol je tel j@s. </event>
      <event start="T700-521" end="T702-029">Vina smo tudi imeli ... </event>
      <event start="T702-029" end="T702-981">Mi ... </event>
      <event start="T704-739" end="T237">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T237" end="T705-868">tam ... </event>
      <event start="T707-483" end="T709-731">Eee tam na na kanč@ n() ma n@nka ne. </event>
      <event start="T709-731" end="T714-868">Eee, na() na šč() na šči() na ščinke smo začeli igrat, [glas] </event>
      <event start="T714-868" end="T716-136">ki smo pršli v Izolo. </event>
      <event start="T716-136" end="T717-609">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T717-609" end="T239">Uondi, k@m@r je bil eee plec. </event>
      <event start="T239" end="T721-109">Plec je bla zemlja. </event>
      <event start="T721-109" end="T726-466">Uondi vs() [smeh] vse() vse take bunkice, ki smo hodili se igrat. </event>
      <event start="T726-466" end="T240">In pol smo se kregali ku hudič, </event>
      <event start="T240" end="T728-455">kaj miš kr taku. </event>
      <event start="T728-455" end="T729-786">Eee eee. </event>
      <event start="T729-786" end="T731-465">Intanto je blo gušto. </event>
      <event start="T751-052" end="T248">Js znam, </event>
      <event start="T248" end="T752-418">ja. </event>
      <event start="T754-191" end="T755-964">Šk() škanjete. </event>
      <event start="T762-132" end="T254">Gotovo. </event>
      <event start="T254" end="T766-121">Tab@t, k je pršu nazaj, se je palo dol sz špoca po() po() po tleh. </event>
      <event start="T777-461" end="T260">[smeh] Ja ja, </event>
      <event start="T260" end="T262">sej je res, </event>
      <event start="T262" end="T779-329">je. </event>
      <event start="T786-034" end="T266">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T266" end="T788-898">mi, k@r se tiče tega, vse vse, kar s tistih stvari ... </event>
      <event start="T788-898" end="T267">Samo jes znam, znam, ki smo meli, </event>
      <event start="T267" end="T268">ja, </event>
      <event start="T268" end="T271">tabot smo meli, </event>
      <event start="T271" end="T272">ja, </event>
      <event start="T272" end="T269">prej ko smo šli v Izolo, </event>
      <event start="T269" end="T270">mogoče je bil pol leta prej ali kej taga, </event>
      <event start="T270" end="T797-050">menj. </event>
      <event start="T797-050" end="T415">Imu moj woče bičikleto, </event>
      <event start="T415" end="T802-991">ki je šu delat ... gor v Šmarje proti Kopri. </event>
      <event start="T802-991" end="T273">Dol, tam so delali, </event>
      <event start="T273" end="T806-170">in so delali cesto za Šmarje. </event>
      <event start="T806-170" end="T807-660">Tabot, neki takega je blo. </event>
      <event start="T807-660" end="T416">Inu je šu </event>
      <event start="T416" end="T274">i svojo bičikleto </event>
      <event start="T274" end="T275">... je p@sto bičikleto doma, </event>
      <event start="T275" end="T811-407">ka znan, kod je bil. </event>
      <event start="T811-407" end="T815-711">In Miha jih peljal gor na, gor na, na na prvo nadstropje v hiši. </event>
      <event start="T815-711" end="T818-558">In mi za se z() v bistvu bl() bičikleto vad@t, </event>
      <event start="T818-558" end="T276">smo vlekli dol na, </event>
      <event start="T276" end="T277">ne vem, na kašn način. </event>
      <event start="T277" end="T826-218">J@s ino [smeh] jaz ino Nevja ... smo vlekli dol, ki nismo mogli. </event>
      <event start="T826-218" end="T828-388">Ku da vzet, bomo navadli sz to bičikleto. </event>
      <event start="T828-388" end="T278">Mama je njurla: </event>
      <event start="T278" end="T279">"Kaj greste dol, </event>
      <event start="T279" end="T280">papa je skr@u gor, </event>
      <event start="T280" end="T417">da ne da ne hodeste z njo, uno, </event>
      <event start="T417" end="T418">da ne padeste, </event>
      <event start="T418" end="T281">da se ne udariste." </event>
      <event start="T281" end="T282">Aaa joj. </event>
      <event start="T282" end="T836-239">Tašne ... </event>
      <event start="T840-754" end="T283">Ne, ne, ne. </event>
      <event start="T283" end="T843-290">To je vse za nas. </event>
      <event start="T843-290" end="T420">To vse za nas blo, </event>
      <event start="T420" end="T845-132">za jest. </event>
      <event start="T845-132" end="T846-289">Vse za nas je blo. </event>
      <event start="T846-890" end="T284">Smo meli po dva, </event>
      <event start="T284" end="T848-711">skuzi po dva. </event>
      <event start="T898-226" end="T898-921">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T901-425" end="T298">[glas] Ja, </event>
      <event start="T298" end="T299">normalno, </event>
      <event start="T299" end="T903-404">ne. </event>
      <event start="T903-404" end="T301">Še tabot pole, ki je blo že preko s() v sss, </event>
      <event start="T301" end="T300">ja, </event>
      <event start="T300" end="T302">še zmer o Jugoslaviji govorimo, </event>
      <event start="T302" end="T303">ne. </event>
      <event start="T303" end="T911-595">In taku. </event>
      <event start="T911-595" end="T912-768">Samo ... </event>
      <event start="T912-768" end="T424">takat, ki je, je bla moja sestra, Ernešta, </event>
      <event start="T424" end="T304">ni bla, mmm ona ni bla maj doma, </event>
      <event start="T304" end="T923-467">@nka k je bla majhna, je šla zmeri nekam proč. </event>
      <event start="T923-467" end="T305">Ne vem, kam je bla, je bla ... </event>
      <event start="T305" end="T306">ne m, je ka proč, </event>
      <event start="T306" end="T926-587">ni bla doma. </event>
      <event start="T926-587" end="T307">In ponjer, ki smo se, ki je pršla že kot pupa, </event>
      <event start="T307" end="T930-027">bi reku. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T930-027" end="T308">So se spoznali sz mojim kunjadom Rugiertom, ki je tudi on pokojni. </event>
      <event start="T308" end="T936-492">Ki je ona tudi zdaj pokojna. </event>
      <event start="T936-492" end="T425">Inu so ... </event>
      <event start="T425" end="T426">on je vozu tabot, </event>
      <event start="T426" end="T943-576">uni, ki so eee vidli okuli filme. </event>
      <event start="T943-576" end="T945-320">Filme. </event>
      <event start="T946-237" end="T946-727">Filme. </event>
      <event start="T946-727" end="T947-167">Je pršu z avtom uni od una. </event>
      <event start="T947-167" end="T951-811">Pršu z avtom skoraj dol du ... du nes. </event>
      <event start="T951-811" end="T310">Ma ne do nes. </event>
      <event start="T310" end="T955-353">Malček spodaj je pršu, do nes. </event>
      <event start="T955-353" end="T311">Inu ki je pršu gor, </event>
      <event start="T311" end="T312">ma so bli pač ko maroži, </event>
      <event start="T312" end="T313">ne. </event>
      <event start="T313" end="T960-319">Je pršu unu. </event>
      <event start="T960-319" end="T314">Inu potem sz nekej cajta taku ... </event>
      <event start="T314" end="T965-575">Njegova sestra Nives tudi je pršla h nan. </event>
      <event start="T965-575" end="T973-027">In mi ko otroci, ki [smeh] nismo te nje poznali, smo se skrivali. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T973-027" end="T315">Smo se skrivali okuli, pr hiši, </event>
      <event start="T315" end="T316">nismo teli se pukazat. </event>
      <event start="T316" end="T978-863">In za kamenjem in podobno. </event>
      <event start="T986-248" end="T318">Ma to to normalno, </event>
      <event start="T318" end="T319">ja, </event>
      <event start="T319" end="T988-322">to. </event>
      <event start="T988-322" end="T320">Ma ne da k(), da k(), da smo kral, </event>
      <event start="T320" end="T990-510">bi reku, </event>
      <event start="T990-510" end="T321">za za lač() za kot lačne. </event>
      <event start="T321" end="T995-321">To je blu eee ena navada. </event>
      <event start="T995-925" end="T322">Alora, </event>
      <event start="T322" end="T997-446">smo bli že veliki. </event>
      <event start="T997-446" end="T323">Že veliki. </event>
      <event start="T323" end="T1000-152">Smo meli petnajst, št@rnajst let, petnajst. </event>
      <event start="T1000-152" end="T324">Ma nismo bivali gor, </event>
      <event start="T324" end="T1002-827">smo bivai v Izoli. </event>
      <event start="T1002-827" end="T325">Ma gor smo meli njive še tabot </event>
      <event start="T325" end="T326">in jes in Dario ... smo šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T326" end="T327">nekej so delali oni, </event>
      <event start="T327" end="T329">nekej š@pcali, </event>
      <event start="T329" end="T427">ka znam, </event>
      <event start="T427" end="T1011-228">ko ene trte, to. </event>
      <event start="T1011-228" end="T328">Woča ni blu. </event>
      <event start="T328" end="T331">Ma, </event>
      <event start="T331" end="T330">in pol nas je blu. </event>
      <event start="T330" end="T332">Pa sem reku: </event>
      <event start="T332" end="T333">"Mi gremo sami." </event>
      <event start="T333" end="T334">Seveda hod@t, </event>
      <event start="T334" end="T335">ne, </event>
      <event start="T335" end="T336">kaj, </event>
      <event start="T336" end="T1017-605">gor, z Izole gor. </event>
      <event start="T1017-605" end="T1019-129">Hodit. </event>
      <event start="T1019-129" end="T1020-090">In pole smo šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T1020-090" end="T337">uoni so pršli zraven. </event>
      <event start="T337" end="T1025-940">Je bil en mož tam, ki je koso ... koso travo v njivi. </event>
      <event start="T1025-940" end="T338">Je bil eee zid taku, </event>
      <event start="T338" end="T339">mi nismo bli visok, </event>
      <event start="T339" end="T1029-384">smo pogleal skuzi zid. </event>
      <event start="T1029-384" end="T1032-359">Inu smo vidli aaa angurije in melone. </event>
      <event start="T1032-359" end="T1034-291">Inu ponjer je, </event>
      <event start="T1034-291" end="T1038-437">uondi zgoraj je j@mu hišo, ki je, ki je, njegova žena. </event>
      <event start="T1038-437" end="T1041-808">Lih ta lih ta žena hodila v Trst, ki je vozila rubo to. </event>
      <event start="T1041-808" end="T1044-655">In on se je klicu Čir, Čir, ta muž. </event>
      <event start="T1044-655" end="T1048-532">"Čir, hodi damu, ki je kosilo." </event>
      <event start="T1048-532" end="T340">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T340" end="T1050-517">pridem, vele, vele." </event>
      <event start="T1050-517" end="T341">[smeh] Je šu domu. </event>
      <event start="T341" end="T342">Mi smo š() [smeh] šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T342" end="T343">je j@mu žakelj, ki je verjetno mislu uon pobr@t melone in tu, </event>
      <event start="T343" end="T1058-588">smo obral mi. </event>
      <event start="T1058-588" end="T1061-220">[smeh] In je dol v staro hišo domu. </event>
      <event start="T1062-282" end="T1067-069">Ma in še z() in ponj je še zmerej je blo ta, ku da bi bla afera. </event>
      <event start="T1067-069" end="T428">Ma da na k@do je bil, </event>
      <event start="T428" end="T429">da kateri so bli, </event>
      <event start="T429" end="T430">da jes nisem vidu, </event>
      <event start="T430" end="T1071-706">da tu. </event>
      <event start="T1071-706" end="T344">In tu, ki je gledu. </event>
      <event start="T344" end="T345">Ka on zna, ku smo kopali uno prej, </event>
      <event start="T345" end="T346">ku smo kopali drug dan, </event>
      <event start="T346" end="T1075-431">n@č. </event>
      <event start="T1075-431" end="T1078-609">D@ so bli eni t@, da on ne zna, kašno podobnu. </event>
      <event start="T1078-609" end="T347">In pol da spet šu v: </event>
      <event start="T347" end="T349">"Ivan, </event>
      <event start="T349" end="T348">ma ka so bli toji otroci ta in ta dan te, te." </event>
      <event start="T348" end="T1084-771">"Ma da jes znam ne, da ..." </event>
      <event start="T1084-771" end="T1085-881">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1085-881" end="T350">Mi smo samo mučali, ki ne smeš povedat n@č. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T350" end="T351">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T351" end="T352">to je taku, </event>
      <event start="T352" end="T353">take stvari so ble, </event>
      <event start="T353" end="T1090-360">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1090-360" end="T1092-853">Inu polej pa smo hodil pobirat češnje. </event>
      <event start="T1092-853" end="T354">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T354" end="T355">ma je tu. </event>
      <event start="T355" end="T356">Ma dama nisi smel jest, </event>
      <event start="T356" end="T1096-732">pobirat je blo za prodat. </event>
      <event start="T1096-732" end="T357">Alora, </event>
      <event start="T357" end="T1098-725">mi smo šli nabrat ... </event>
      <event start="T1100-578" end="T1101-858">Mi smo šli do enga druzga. </event>
      <event start="T1101-858" end="T1103-970">Jest, do ene druge. </event>
      <event start="T1103-970" end="T358">In uonde je bla ena češnja zraven hiše, </event>
      <event start="T358" end="T1107-264">malo več tan deleč. </event>
      <event start="T1107-264" end="T1112-723">A ena hiša je so bli te ljudje, ki smo jim rekli Pr Ravi, Otavijo, una, una. </event>
      <event start="T1112-723" end="T359">So bli gor. </event>
      <event start="T359" end="T431">Uni so bli gor, </event>
      <event start="T431" end="T1116-128">z gor se je vidlu lepo dol to češnjo. </event>
      <event start="T1116-128" end="T1118-093">Una je bla tude bolj zgodnja češnja. </event>
      <event start="T1118-093" end="T360">[glas] Sm reku zdej: </event>
      <event start="T360" end="T361">"Kaku mi gremo na to češnjo? </event>
      <event start="T361" end="T362">Ki je gor, </event>
      <event start="T362" end="T363">glej ga rod, </event>
      <event start="T363" end="T1122-985">nonštop." </event>
      <event start="T1122-985" end="T364">Dol, </event>
      <event start="T364" end="T1128-041">niso zdej ... s korte proč samo gledali to češnjo. </event>
      <event start="T1128-041" end="T432">In na žleb </event>
      <event start="T432" end="T365">inu pole smo šli, </event>
      <event start="T365" end="T1131-553">kaj smo zeli, en drat. </event>
      <event start="T1131-553" end="T366">En drat. </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T367">In smo se vseli, ki je bla taku korona, </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T368">češnja je bla nad korono. </event>
      <event start="T368" end="T1137-771">Smo vzel en drat. </event>
      <event start="T1137-771" end="T369">[nerazumljivo] Povlekli vejo dol </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T1143-014">inu inu inu jeli. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1143-014" end="T370">Ma smo čuli gor, ki je s() krčala, ta njihova mat: </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T433">"Čuj, čuj, </event>
      <event start="T433" end="T434">Otavijo, Otavijo, </event>
      <event start="T434" end="T1148-536">hoj les. </event>
      <event start="T1148-536" end="T371">Dol p(), dol na češnji neki se juga." </event>
      <event start="T371" end="T1151-705">"Ma kaj ne viš, da piha burja?" </event>
      <event start="T1151-705" end="T1152-878">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1152-878" end="T1154-610">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1159-179" end="T377">Jes se ga, jes se ne spunem, </event>
      <event start="T377" end="T1162-203">jes se spunem zmerem ne eee ... </event>
      <event start="T1162-203" end="T1164-870">eee ne žejen, ne lačen. </event>
      <event start="T1164-870" end="T379">Vesel. </event>
      <event start="T379" end="T435">Evo </event>
      <event start="T435" end="T380">veselje je blo tabot, </event>
      <event start="T380" end="T1167-486">gotovo. </event>
      <event start="T1167-486" end="T1168-608">Mar si bil bos i nag. </event>
      <event start="T1168-608" end="T1170-198">Tabot. </event>
      <event start="T1171-478" end="T1172-092">Ja. </event>
    </tier>
    <tier id="TIE2_NORM1" speaker="ROG-dialog-0030" category="norm" type="t" display-name="ROG-dialog-0030 [norm]">
      <event start="T14-586" end="T15-238">Seveda. </event>
      <event start="T15-238" end="T8">Kmetje smo bili, kmetje, </event>
      <event start="T8" end="T3">in to polno. </event>
      <event start="T3" end="T4">Kmeti in polno otrok. </event>
      <event start="T4" end="T19-117">Kaj. </event>
      <event start="T22-104" end="T23-340">Osem, devet, deset. </event>
      <event start="T40-955" end="T44-246">Tabot, ki se spomnim jaz, se spomnim jaz, k nas je bilo štiri. </event>
      <event start="T44-246" end="T21">Kompena štiri, </event>
      <event start="T21" end="T22">govorimo, </event>
      <event start="T22" end="T45-983">ne. </event>
      <event start="T45-983" end="T47-205">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T47-205" end="T48-931">Smo spali v kaštinah od ramarona. </event>
      <event start="T51-984" end="T53-375">En, dva, tri, štiri. </event>
      <event start="T55-936" end="T56-726">En, dva, tri, štiri. </event>
      <event start="T64-749" end="T65-745">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T68-258" end="T28">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T28" end="T69-051">normalno to, </event>
      <event start="T69-051" end="T69-399">ja. </event>
