      <event start="T704-739" end="T237">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T237" end="T705-868">tam ... </event>
      <event start="T707-483" end="T709-731">Eee tam na na kanče n() ma nanka ne. </event>
      <event start="T709-731" end="T714-868">Eee, na() na šč() na šči() na ščinke smo začeli igrati, [glas] </event>
      <event start="T714-868" end="T716-136">ki smo prišli v Izolo. </event>
      <event start="T716-136" end="T717-609">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T717-609" end="T239">Ondi, kamor je bil eee plac. </event>
      <event start="T239" end="T721-109">Plac je bila zemlja. </event>
      <event start="T721-109" end="T726-466">Ondi vs() [smeh] vse() vse take bunkice, ki smo hodili se igrat. </event>
      <event start="T726-466" end="T240">In pol smo se kregali ku hudič, </event>
      <event start="T240" end="T728-455">kaj misliš kar tako. </event>
      <event start="T728-455" end="T729-786">Eee eee. </event>
      <event start="T729-786" end="T731-465">Intanto je bilo gušto. </event>
      <event start="T751-052" end="T248">Jaz znam, </event>
      <event start="T248" end="T752-418">ja. </event>
      <event start="T754-191" end="T755-964">Šk() škanjete. </event>
      <event start="T762-132" end="T254">Gotovo. </event>
      <event start="T254" end="T766-121">Tabat, k je prišel nazaj, se je padlo dol sz špoca po() po() po tleh. </event>
      <event start="T777-461" end="T260">[smeh] Ja ja, </event>
      <event start="T260" end="T262">saj je res, </event>
      <event start="T262" end="T779-329">je. </event>
      <event start="T786-034" end="T266">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T266" end="T788-898">mi, kar se tiče tega, vse vse, kar s tistih stvari ... </event>
      <event start="T788-898" end="T267">Samo jaz znam, znam, ki smo imeli, </event>
      <event start="T267" end="T268">ja, </event>
      <event start="T268" end="T271">tabot smo imeli, </event>
      <event start="T271" end="T272">ja, </event>
      <event start="T272" end="T269">prej ko smo šli v Izolo, </event>
      <event start="T269" end="T270">mogoče je bil pol leta prej ali kaj takega, </event>
      <event start="T270" end="T797-050">manj. </event>
      <event start="T797-050" end="T415">Inu moj oče bičikleto, </event>
      <event start="T415" end="T802-991">ki je šel delat ... gor v Šmarje proti Kopru. </event>
      <event start="T802-991" end="T273">Dol, tam so delali, </event>
      <event start="T273" end="T806-170">in so delali cesto za Šmarje. </event>
      <event start="T806-170" end="T807-660">Tabot, nekaj takega je bilo. </event>
      <event start="T807-660" end="T416">Inu je šel </event>
      <event start="T416" end="T274">in svojo bičikleto </event>
      <event start="T274" end="T275">... je pustil bičikleto doma, </event>
      <event start="T275" end="T811-407">kaj znam, kod je bil. </event>
      <event start="T811-407" end="T815-711">In Miha jih peljal gor na, gor na, na na prvo nadstropje v hiši. </event>
      <event start="T815-711" end="T818-558">In mi za se z() v bistvu bl() bičikleto vadit, </event>
      <event start="T818-558" end="T276">smo vlekli dol na, </event>
      <event start="T276" end="T277">ne vem, na kakšen način. </event>
      <event start="T277" end="T826-218">Jaz inu [smeh] jaz inu Nevja ... smo vlekli dol, ki nismo mogli. </event>
      <event start="T826-218" end="T828-388">Ku da vzeti, bomo navadili sz to bičikleto. </event>
      <event start="T828-388" end="T278">Mama je njurila: </event>
      <event start="T278" end="T279">"Kaj greste dol, </event>
      <event start="T279" end="T280">papa je skril gor, </event>
      <event start="T280" end="T417">da ne da ne hodite z njo, ono, </event>
      <event start="T417" end="T418">da ne padete, </event>
      <event start="T418" end="T281">da se ne udarite." </event>
      <event start="T281" end="T282">Aaa joj. </event>
      <event start="T282" end="T836-239">Takšne ... </event>
      <event start="T840-754" end="T283">Ne, ne, ne. </event>
      <event start="T283" end="T843-290">To je vse za nas. </event>
      <event start="T843-290" end="T420">To vse za nas bilo, </event>
      <event start="T420" end="T845-132">za jesti. </event>
      <event start="T845-132" end="T846-289">Vse za nas je bilo. </event>
      <event start="T846-890" end="T284">Smo imeli po dva, </event>
      <event start="T284" end="T848-711">skozi po dva. </event>
      <event start="T898-226" end="T898-921">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T901-425" end="T298">[glas] Ja, </event>
      <event start="T298" end="T299">normalno, </event>
      <event start="T299" end="T903-404">ne. </event>
      <event start="T903-404" end="T301">Še tabot pol, ki je bilo že preko s() v sss, </event>
      <event start="T301" end="T300">ja, </event>
      <event start="T300" end="T302">še zmeraj o Jugoslaviji govorimo, </event>
      <event start="T302" end="T303">ne. </event>
      <event start="T303" end="T911-595">In tako. </event>
      <event start="T911-595" end="T912-768">Samo ... </event>
      <event start="T912-768" end="T424">takrat, ki je, je bila moja sestra, Ernešta, </event>
      <event start="T424" end="T304">ni bila, mmm ona ni bila maj doma, </event>
      <event start="T304" end="T923-467">anka k je bila majhna, je šla zmeraj nekam proč. </event>
      <event start="T923-467" end="T305">Ne vem, kam je bila, je bila ... </event>
      <event start="T305" end="T306">ne vem, je kaj proč, </event>
      <event start="T306" end="T926-587">ni bila doma. </event>
      <event start="T926-587" end="T307">In ponjer, ki smo se, ki je prišla že kot pupa, </event>
      <event start="T307" end="T930-027">bi rekel. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T930-027" end="T308">So se spoznali sz mojim kunjadom Rugiertom, ki je tudi on pokojni. </event>
      <event start="T308" end="T936-492">Ki je ona tudi zdaj pokojna. </event>
      <event start="T936-492" end="T425">Inu so ... </event>
      <event start="T425" end="T426">on je vozil tabot, </event>
      <event start="T426" end="T943-576">oni, ki so eee videli okoli filme. </event>
      <event start="T943-576" end="T945-320">Filme. </event>
      <event start="T946-237" end="T946-727">Filme. </event>
      <event start="T946-727" end="T947-167">Je prišel z avtom oni od ona. </event>
      <event start="T947-167" end="T951-811">Prišel z avtom skoraj dol do ... do nas. </event>
      <event start="T951-811" end="T310">Ma ne do nas. </event>
      <event start="T310" end="T955-353">Malček spodaj je prišel, do nas. </event>
      <event start="T955-353" end="T311">Inu ki je prišel gor, </event>
      <event start="T311" end="T312">ma so bili pač ko maroži, </event>
      <event start="T312" end="T313">ne. </event>
      <event start="T313" end="T960-319">Je prišel ono. </event>
      <event start="T960-319" end="T314">Inu potem sz nekaj cajta tako ... </event>
      <event start="T314" end="T965-575">Njegova sestra Nives tudi je prišla k nam. </event>
      <event start="T965-575" end="T973-027">In mi kot otroci, ki [smeh] nismo te nje poznali, smo se skrivali. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T973-027" end="T315">Smo se skrivali okoli, pri hiši, </event>
      <event start="T315" end="T316">nismo hoteli se pokazati. </event>
      <event start="T316" end="T978-863">In za kamenjem in podobno. </event>
      <event start="T986-248" end="T318">Ma to to normalno, </event>
      <event start="T318" end="T319">ja, </event>
      <event start="T319" end="T988-322">to. </event>
      <event start="T988-322" end="T320">Ma ne da k(), da k(), da smo kradli, </event>
      <event start="T320" end="T990-510">bi rekel, </event>
      <event start="T990-510" end="T321">za za lač() za kot lačne. </event>
      <event start="T321" end="T995-321">To je bilo eee ena navada. </event>
      <event start="T995-925" end="T322">Alora, </event>
      <event start="T322" end="T997-446">smo bili že veliki. </event>
      <event start="T997-446" end="T323">Že veliki. </event>
      <event start="T323" end="T1000-152">Smo imeli petnajst, štirinajst let, petnajst. </event>
      <event start="T1000-152" end="T324">Ma nismo bivali gor, </event>
      <event start="T324" end="T1002-827">smo bivali v Izoli. </event>
      <event start="T1002-827" end="T325">Ma gor smo imeli njive še tabot </event>
      <event start="T325" end="T326">in jaz in Dario ... smo šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T326" end="T327">nekaj so delali oni, </event>
      <event start="T327" end="T329">nekaj šepcali, </event>
      <event start="T329" end="T427">kaj znam, </event>
      <event start="T427" end="T1011-228">ko ene trte, to. </event>
      <event start="T1011-228" end="T328">Oča ni bilo. </event>
      <event start="T328" end="T331">Ma, </event>
      <event start="T331" end="T330">in pol nas je bilo. </event>
      <event start="T330" end="T332">Pa sem rekel: </event>
      <event start="T332" end="T333">"Mi gremo sami." </event>
      <event start="T333" end="T334">Seveda hodit, </event>
      <event start="T334" end="T335">ne, </event>
      <event start="T335" end="T336">kaj, </event>
      <event start="T336" end="T1017-605">gor, z Izole gor. </event>
      <event start="T1017-605" end="T1019-129">Hodit. </event>
      <event start="T1019-129" end="T1020-090">In pol smo šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T1020-090" end="T337">oni so prišli zraven. </event>
      <event start="T337" end="T1025-940">Je bil en mož tam, ki je kosil ... kosil travo v njivi. </event>
      <event start="T1025-940" end="T338">Je bil eee zid tako, </event>
      <event start="T338" end="T339">mi nismo bili visoki, </event>
      <event start="T339" end="T1029-384">smo pogledali skozi zid. </event>
      <event start="T1029-384" end="T1032-359">Inu smo videli aaa angurije in melone. </event>
      <event start="T1032-359" end="T1034-291">Inu ponjer je, </event>
      <event start="T1034-291" end="T1038-437">ondi zgoraj je imel hišo, ki je, ki je, njegova žena. </event>
      <event start="T1038-437" end="T1041-808">Glih ta glih ta žena hodila v Trst, ki je vozila robo to. </event>
      <event start="T1041-808" end="T1044-655">In on se je klical Čir, Čir, ta mož. </event>
      <event start="T1044-655" end="T1048-532">"Čir, hodi domov, ki je kosilo." </event>
      <event start="T1048-532" end="T340">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T340" end="T1050-517">pridem, vele, vele." </event>
      <event start="T1050-517" end="T341">[smeh] Je šel domov. </event>
      <event start="T341" end="T342">Mi smo š() [smeh] šli gor, </event>
      <event start="T342" end="T343">je imel žakelj, ki je verjetno mislil on pobrati melone in to, </event>
      <event start="T343" end="T1058-588">smo obrali mi. </event>
      <event start="T1058-588" end="T1061-220">[smeh] In je dol v staro hišo domov. </event>
      <event start="T1062-282" end="T1067-069">Ma in še z() in ponj je še zmeraj je bilo ta, ku da bi bila afera. </event>
      <event start="T1067-069" end="T428">Ma da na kdo je bil, </event>
      <event start="T428" end="T429">da kateri so bili, </event>
      <event start="T429" end="T430">da jaz nisem videl, </event>
      <event start="T430" end="T1071-706">da to. </event>
      <event start="T1071-706" end="T344">In to, ki je gledal. </event>
      <event start="T344" end="T345">Kaj on zna, ku smo kopali ono prej, </event>
      <event start="T345" end="T346">ku smo kopali drug dan, </event>
      <event start="T346" end="T1075-431">nič. </event>
      <event start="T1075-431" end="T1078-609">Da so bili eni to, da on ne zna, kakšno podobno. </event>
      <event start="T1078-609" end="T347">In pol da spet šel v: </event>
      <event start="T347" end="T349">"Ivan, </event>
      <event start="T349" end="T348">ma kaj so bili tvoji otroci ta in ta dan te, te." </event>
      <event start="T348" end="T1084-771">"Ma da jaz znam ne, da ..." </event>
      <event start="T1084-771" end="T1085-881">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1085-881" end="T350">Mi smo samo molčali, ki ne smeš povedati nič. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T350" end="T351">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T351" end="T352">to je tako, </event>
      <event start="T352" end="T353">take stvari so bile, </event>
      <event start="T353" end="T1090-360">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1090-360" end="T1092-853">Inu pol pa smo hodili pobirat češnje. </event>
      <event start="T1092-853" end="T354">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T354" end="T355">ma je to. </event>
      <event start="T355" end="T356">Ma doma nisi smel jesti, </event>
      <event start="T356" end="T1096-732">pobirati je bilo za prodati. </event>
      <event start="T1096-732" end="T357">Alora, </event>
      <event start="T357" end="T1098-725">mi smo šli nabrat ... </event>
      <event start="T1100-578" end="T1101-858">Mi smo šli do enega drugega. </event>
      <event start="T1101-858" end="T1103-970">Jest, do ene druge. </event>
      <event start="T1103-970" end="T358">In onde je bila ena češnja zraven hiše, </event>
      <event start="T358" end="T1107-264">malo več tam daleč. </event>
      <event start="T1107-264" end="T1112-723">A ena hiša je so bili ti ljudje, ki smo jim rekli Pri Ravi, Ottavio, ona, ona. </event>
      <event start="T1112-723" end="T359">So bili gor. </event>
      <event start="T359" end="T431">Oni so bili gor, </event>
      <event start="T431" end="T1116-128">z gor se je videlo lepo dol to češnjo. </event>
      <event start="T1116-128" end="T1118-093">Ona je bila tudi bolj zgodnja češnja. </event>
      <event start="T1118-093" end="T360">[glas] Sem rekel zdaj: </event>
      <event start="T360" end="T361">"Kako mi gremo na to češnjo? </event>
      <event start="T361" end="T362">Ki je gor, </event>
      <event start="T362" end="T363">glej ga rod, </event>
      <event start="T363" end="T1122-985">nonstop." </event>
      <event start="T1122-985" end="T364">Dol, </event>
      <event start="T364" end="T1128-041">niso zdaj ... s korte proč samo gledali to češnjo. </event>
      <event start="T1128-041" end="T432">In na žleb </event>
      <event start="T432" end="T365">inu pol smo šli, </event>
      <event start="T365" end="T1131-553">kaj smo vzeli, en drat. </event>
      <event start="T1131-553" end="T366">En drat. </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T367">In smo se vsedli, ki je bila tako korona, </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T368">češnja je bila nad korono. </event>
      <event start="T368" end="T1137-771">Smo vzeli en drat. </event>
      <event start="T1137-771" end="T369">[nerazumljivo] Povlekli vejo dol </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T1143-014">inu inu inu jedli. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1143-014" end="T370">Ma smo čuli gor, ki je s() kričala, ta njihova mat: </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T433">"Čuj, čuj, </event>
      <event start="T433" end="T434">Otavijo, Otavijo, </event>
      <event start="T434" end="T1148-536">hoj les. </event>
      <event start="T1148-536" end="T371">Dol p(), dol na češnji nekaj se juga." </event>
      <event start="T371" end="T1151-705">"Ma kaj ne vidiš, da piha burja?" </event>
      <event start="T1151-705" end="T1152-878">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1152-878" end="T1154-610">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1159-179" end="T377">Jaz se ga, jaz se ne spomnim, </event>
      <event start="T377" end="T1162-203">jaz se spomnim zmerom ne eee ... </event>
      <event start="T1162-203" end="T1164-870">eee ne žejen, ne lačen. </event>
      <event start="T1164-870" end="T379">Vesel. </event>
      <event start="T379" end="T435">Evo, </event>
      <event start="T435" end="T380">veselje je bilo tabot, </event>
      <event start="T380" end="T1167-486">gotovo. </event>
      <event start="T1167-486" end="T1168-608">Mar si bil bos in nag. </event>
      <event start="T1168-608" end="T1170-198">Tabot. </event>
      <event start="T1171-478" end="T1172-092">Ja. </event>
    </tier>
